    "metaDescription": "ProPresenter is the #1 presentation software for church production — not because of marketing, but because no other tool handles the real complexity of live worship. An honest breakdown from a broadcast integrator.",
    "excerpt": "I don't have an affiliate deal with Renewed Vision. I recommend ProPresenter because it's the right tool — and after 15 years of building church production systems, I've watched every alternative fall short in ways that matter during a live service.",
